title: (x) Please, someone, ID this font! / 'Living Health' - probably custom, similar to ITC Benguiat {Florian}
author: AlysonDeMichele

comments.content:
Hi Alyson,  
welcome to Typophile!

This is probably a custom designed logo, inspired by [ITC Benguiat](http://web.archive.org/web/20100329014347/http:/new.myfonts.com/fonts/adobe/itc-benguiat/?testdrive=custom%3D0%26dock%3Dfalse%26size%3D52%26w%3D600%26src%3Dcustom%26text%3DLIVING%2520HEALTH%26fg%3D000000%26bg%3Dffffff%26goodies%3Dfit%26seed%3D26?refby=mfde). As far as I know, there is no Benguiat Condensed.  
F
Thanks a bunch, I see what you mean. I will use the font you suggested!
